{"tid":1057143,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓第一男團將於4月12日攜新專回歸！！","createTime":"2019-03-11T16:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T09:57:42.000Z","uid":231132,"like":10,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1586e660630652fe21ffaa771a49f70098f6c519","tid":1057143,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"今日防彈少年團方面通過官方SNS表示，將於4月12日發表新專 <em>Map of the Soul: Persona</em>，據悉這是BTS繼去年8月24日發表後續專後，時隔約7個月的回歸。<br />\n<br />\n這張專輯將標誌著BTS的新篇章，這是他們去年夏天完成了他們的Love Yourself專輯三部曲之後的新發行，先前BTS已先後二次進入Billboard 200，首先是五月的Love Yourself:Tear，然後是八月的Love Yourself:Answer。<br />\n<br />\n <em>Map of the Soul: Persona</em>會在即將到來的&ldquo;Love Yourself: Speak Yourself&rdquo;世界巡迴演唱會之前發布，他們會將演出帶到整個北美洲和南美洲，歐洲和亞洲的體育館。歐洲和美國的每場演出都已售罄，其中包括在倫敦標誌性的溫布萊球場舉辦的兩場演唱會。"},{"pid":"9faab1a0e00d7200fe9653f9efad599b9d099986","tid":1057143,"uid":43061,"like":13,"dislike":10,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T16:25:19.000Z","msg":"要不是bb ,有撚人識you bts咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49de5c2a53996546d51a50f62e88b4785fa5702a","tid":1057143,"uid":231132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9faab1a0e00d7200fe9653f9efad599b9d099986","tid":1057143,"uid":43061,"like":13,"dislike":10,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T16:25:19.000Z","msg":"要不是bb ,有撚人識you bts咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T16:27:13.000Z","msg":"咪引戰"},{"pid":"fefcfe469f0879635558ff680a58fec0ae534b52","tid":1057143,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T16:29:59.000Z","msg":"香港army準備好買爆香港所有現貨未！？(๑&bull;̀ㅂ&bull;́)و✧"},{"pid":"2ccec1419664f231a80688ae1e362a3cde099420","tid":1057143,"uid":113773,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T16:33:58.000Z","msg":"好撚中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a40694f64ad73f6485c5c72afc22a52b68e4eb","tid":1057143,"ui